headline: Carnival price target raised to $30 from $28 at Citi
summary: Citi raised the firm’s price target on Carnival (CCL) to $30 from $28 and keeps a Buy rating on the shares. The firm says its most recent work on the cruise industry points to ongoing positive trends, “albeit with pockets of sequential weakness” in web traffic to start the month of December. Consumer interest in cruises remained consistently strong throughout 2023 and into 2024, with trends showing stable second half of 2024 trends after having slowed somewhat after a strong Wave Season earlier
